1
00:00:02,544 --> 00:00:03,306
Body care.

2
00:00:04,527 --> 00:00:07,990
Offering metta, goodwill, loving-kindness to the body.

3
00:00:09,493 --> 00:00:13,217
Remember you can stop the tape any time to develop a particular section.

4
00:00:15,099 --> 00:00:18,161
First we need to undermine the wrong relationship we have to the body.

5
00:00:18,783 --> 00:00:20,403
We think it to be me or mine.

6
00:00:21,705 --> 00:00:27,832
As we weaken this identity and possession, so we can develop a more wholesome, skillful relationship.

7
00:00:30,295 --> 00:00:31,876
Working first with possession.

8
00:00:32,902 --> 00:00:37,591
We hold on to what we like, we discard, we don't look at what we dislike.

9
00:00:40,034 --> 00:00:45,985
Bringing to mind a part of the body that disgusts us to some extent, here's some of the Buddha's own list.

10
00:00:46,646 --> 00:00:52,015
Fishes, bile, pus, blood, sweat, fat, urine.

11
00:00:53,378 --> 00:00:58,067
Choose something, something to get in touch with, to feel that disgust.

12
00:01:18,888 --> 00:01:23,295
Now change your perspective and see it from a biological point of view.

13
00:01:40,302 --> 00:01:43,849
Perhaps your feelings are changing to equanimity, even interest.

14
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:50,621
Now take a part of the body you dislike because it's ugly.

15
00:01:51,543 --> 00:01:54,346
Too thin, too fat, too long, too short, so on.

16
00:01:55,448 --> 00:01:57,831
Again, get in touch with that feeling of dislike.

17
00:02:13,532 --> 00:02:16,215
Beauty and ugliness come from the judgmental mind.

18
00:02:16,987 --> 00:02:18,850
Can't things be just okay as they are?

19
00:02:28,989 --> 00:02:32,634
See if you can turn towards those parts with the heart of acceptance.

20
00:02:44,984 --> 00:02:47,590
Finally, there are those parts that bring us great pleasure.

21
00:02:48,412 --> 00:02:50,135
Take any of the five senses, for instance.

22
00:02:51,117 --> 00:02:56,530
Consider now suffering from an impairment or loss of one of them, say hearing or sight.

23
00:03:16,033 --> 00:03:21,461
As we know from people with disabilities, it doesn't mean we couldn't live equally fulfilling lives.

24
00:03:22,463 --> 00:03:31,717
So we can see that such suffering comes from attachment.

25
00:03:31,737 --> 00:03:34,342
Now let us work a little with the delusion of identity.

26
00:03:35,544 --> 00:03:41,112
Here we can use the three contemplations that awoke the Buddha-to-be to his search for the end of suffering.

27
00:03:41,902 --> 00:03:46,169
repeating each phrase in the heart and accepting its truth value.

28
00:03:48,092 --> 00:03:55,064
First, to undermine our obsession and intoxication with health.

29
00:03:55,085 --> 00:03:57,348
This body is subject to disease.

30
00:04:03,318 --> 00:04:05,902
This body is of a nature to fall ill.

31
00:04:12,312 --> 00:04:14,876
This body has not gone beyond sickness.

32
00:04:22,627 --> 00:04:26,593
Now to undermine our obsession and intoxication with youthfulness.

33
00:04:28,836 --> 00:04:30,699
This body is subject to aging.

34
00:04:36,369 --> 00:04:39,112
This body has not gone beyond aging.

35
00:04:45,235 --> 00:04:48,158
This body is now in a process of aging.

36
00:04:55,771 --> 00:04:59,557
And now to undermine our obsession and intoxication with life itself.

37
00:05:02,461 --> 00:05:04,223
This body is subject to death.

38
00:05:11,314 --> 00:05:13,216
This body has not gone beyond death.

39
00:05:18,850 --> 00:05:20,793
this body will die.

40
00:05:20,833 --> 00:05:32,531
Having undermined to some extent the wrong relationship we have to the body, we can now develop a right relationship.

41
00:05:33,913 --> 00:05:36,016
The Buddha said this was a precious rebirth.

42
00:05:36,596 --> 00:05:41,685
Here we experience joy and woe and we have the intelligence to rise above them.

43
00:05:43,668 --> 00:05:45,329
Firstly, we can't be here without a body.

44
00:05:45,389 --> 00:05:46,512
It's as simple as that.

45
00:05:48,196 --> 00:05:51,319
Secondly, it's through the senses that we experience the world and learn.

46
00:05:53,521 --> 00:05:57,204
Thirdly, it's through the body we relate, communicate and express ourselves.

47
00:05:59,528 --> 00:06:05,733
And finally, in this tradition, it's through the very breath of the body that we can develop the spiritual faculties.

48
00:06:08,916 --> 00:06:14,041
Once we realise how precious the body really is, we can't but want to care for it.

49
00:06:15,324 --> 00:06:16,785
Now, we haven't done so in the past,

50
00:06:17,237 --> 00:06:26,168
So before we can offer it, loving kindness, let us apologise for all the rough times we've given it and perhaps are still giving it.

51
00:06:30,572 --> 00:06:44,307
Whatever harm I have done to you in thought, word and deed, by way of greed, hatred and delusion, intentionally or unintentionally, I'm heartily sorry for it.

52
00:06:45,317 --> 00:06:50,423
and I determine from this day on to treat you with due care and respect.

53
00:06:55,649 --> 00:06:58,213
So now we can begin to offer our blessings to the body.

54
00:06:59,435 --> 00:07:03,218
Choose a phrase which expresses for you healing or well-being.

55
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:08,305
Place it in the heart and offer that blessing to the whole body.

56
00:07:22,932 --> 00:07:30,281
Now it may be that you see light or feel heat, all well and good, but there's no need for such manifestations as such.

57
00:07:30,903 --> 00:07:36,451
What is working for us is our acts of will, our intentioned intentions.

58
00:07:39,574 --> 00:07:45,142
So now let's take our time and go through the whole body from the top of the head to the tip of the toes.

59
00:07:48,528 --> 00:07:52,213
Starting at the hair and scalp, offer your blessings there.

60
00:07:57,576 --> 00:08:00,721
Come down into the brain and fill it with loving-kindness.

61
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:16,240
Bless your eyes and your ears.

62
00:08:22,769 --> 00:08:25,692
Bless your nose and nasal cavities.

63
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:36,344
Bless your mouth with its tongue, teeth, lips.

64
00:08:46,298 --> 00:08:46,940
The jaw.

65
00:08:55,812 --> 00:08:59,798
Pour your blessing into your throat, the precious voice box.

66
00:09:08,822 --> 00:09:14,791
so that the whole head feels warmed and energised.

67
00:09:14,811 --> 00:09:17,294
May you be free of sickness and disease.

68
00:09:18,517 --> 00:09:21,159
May you be well and strong.

69
00:09:26,167 --> 00:09:33,136
Turning our attention now to the top of the spine and make your way down, offering each vertebrae your blessing.

70
00:09:36,542 --> 00:09:37,462
Come down the neck.

71
00:09:46,554 --> 00:10:12,899
down the back down the small of the back down to the very tip

72
00:10:22,802 --> 00:10:25,826
so the whole spine feels warmed and energized.

73
00:10:26,868 --> 00:10:29,451
May you be free of sickness and disease.

74
00:10:30,250 --> 00:10:32,234
May you be well and strong.

75
00:10:36,197 --> 00:10:40,802
Starting at the left shoulder, massage it with loving kindness.

76
00:10:47,811 --> 00:10:50,193
And make your way down towards the elbow.

77
00:11:00,096 --> 00:11:01,578
Down towards the wrist.

78
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:15,721
And into the hand.

79
00:11:17,124 --> 00:11:20,669
Massage your hand with warm loving kindness.

80
00:11:31,702 --> 00:11:34,628
So the whole arm feels warmed and energized.

81
00:11:35,950 --> 00:11:38,355
May you be free of sickness and disease.

82
00:11:40,097 --> 00:11:41,539
May you be well and strong.

83
00:11:46,688 --> 00:11:48,172
Moving to the right shoulder.

84
00:11:49,453 --> 00:11:52,799
Again, massage it with loving kindness.

85
00:12:03,091 --> 00:12:05,114
Making our way down to the elbow.

86
00:12:05,153 --> 00:12:20,677
Down to the wrist.

87
00:12:32,234 --> 00:12:33,394
and into the hand.

88
00:12:34,496 --> 00:12:37,880
Massage your hand with warm, loving kindness.

89
00:12:51,037 --> 00:12:53,679
So the whole arm feels warmed and energized.

90
00:12:54,581 --> 00:12:57,485
May you be free of sickness and disease.

91
00:12:58,385 --> 00:13:01,009
May you be well and strong.

92
00:13:07,115 --> 00:13:09,581
Turning our attention now to the chest area.

93
00:13:12,089 --> 00:13:19,470
Now you can either offer your blessings to particular organs or you can just fill that felt space with loving-kindness.

94
00:13:41,017 --> 00:13:44,302
So the whole chest feels warmed and energized.

95
00:13:48,168 --> 00:13:50,610
May you be free of sickness and disease.

96
00:13:51,852 --> 00:13:53,916
May you be well and strong.

97
00:13:57,041 --> 00:13:59,344
Moving down to the midriff, the stomach area.

98
00:14:00,304 --> 00:14:04,071
Again, fill that area with warm, loving kindness.

99
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:30,344
So the whole area feels warmed and energized.

100
00:14:31,625 --> 00:14:34,210
May you be free of sickness and disease.

101
00:14:34,931 --> 00:14:37,114
May you be well and strong.

102
00:14:42,321 --> 00:14:45,586
Moving down into the abdomen with all its varied systems.

103
00:14:46,707 --> 00:14:47,990
Offer your blessings there.

104
00:14:48,470 --> 00:14:51,033
Fill that area with warm, loving kindness.

105
00:15:12,394 --> 00:15:19,107
Though the whole area feels warmed and energized, may you be free of sickness and disease.

106
00:15:19,990 --> 00:15:22,033
May you be well and strong.

107
00:15:28,927 --> 00:15:30,190
Moving to the left hip.

108
00:15:31,953 --> 00:15:33,998
Massage it with loving-kindness.

109
00:15:44,996 --> 00:16:13,231
making our way down to the knee and down to the ankle and down to the foot

110
00:16:15,743 --> 00:16:19,447
Massage your foot with warm, loving kindness.

111
00:16:31,158 --> 00:16:33,961
So the whole leg feels warmed and energized.

112
00:16:34,942 --> 00:16:37,904
May you be free of sickness and disease.

113
00:16:39,025 --> 00:16:41,227
May you be well and strong.

114
00:16:46,708 --> 00:16:47,932
Moving to the right hip.

115
00:16:49,134 --> 00:16:50,297
Offer your blessing there.

116
00:17:05,367 --> 00:17:07,553
And making your way down to the knee.

117
00:17:19,378 --> 00:17:20,780
And down to the ankle.

118
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:36,840
And into the foot.

119
00:17:38,001 --> 00:17:41,286
Massage your foot with warm loving kindness.

120
00:17:55,423 --> 00:17:57,865
So the whole leg feels warmed and energised.

121
00:17:59,107 --> 00:18:01,690
May you be free of sickness and disease.

122
00:18:01,990 --> 00:18:03,893
May you be well and strong.

123
00:18:08,978 --> 00:18:12,320
So now we fill the whole body with warm blessings.

124
00:18:13,843 --> 00:18:16,965
Now perhaps there's a part of the body that needs special attention.

125
00:18:17,586 --> 00:18:24,012
Go there now and spend a while filling that area with goodwill, loving-kindness.

126
00:18:39,046 --> 00:18:49,281
So now it's time to open ourselves up to whatever source of energy there is in the universe, using a method taken from the Tibetan tradition of the Medicine Buddha.

127
00:18:51,846 --> 00:18:55,191
Imagine there's a golden light descending upon you from above.

128
00:18:56,272 --> 00:19:00,720
Remember, any color will do, which you feel is healing or energizing.

129
00:19:02,722 --> 00:19:07,230
And as it pours down, it begins to form a ball just above your head.

130
00:19:13,605 --> 00:19:16,730
Don't worry if the image is not strong.

131
00:19:20,556 --> 00:19:32,753
Let it pour down until the ball takes on the feel of warm water, the consistency of warm water, and it slowly begins to rotate on itself.

132
00:19:37,861 --> 00:19:41,807
Still pouring down from above, the ball gets heavier.

133
00:19:43,660 --> 00:19:46,644
and we can begin to feel it upon our scalps.

134
00:19:49,087 --> 00:20:08,396
Let it slowly descend down through the scalp, gently rotating, feeling it over the forehead and the back of the head, descending into the brain, filling it with that warm, vibrant energy.

135
00:20:11,361 --> 00:20:13,144
Feel it enter into our eyes,

136
00:20:18,355 --> 00:20:19,256
And ears.

137
00:20:25,462 --> 00:20:32,790
Feel his energy and warmth entering into your nose and nasal cavities.

138
00:20:34,593 --> 00:20:36,654
Slowly, gently rotating.

139
00:20:39,377 --> 00:20:41,460
Still pouring down from above.

140
00:20:46,367 --> 00:20:50,214
And we can feel its energy now entering into our mouths.

141
00:20:54,883 --> 00:20:58,048
Filling our mouths with its warm golden energy.

142
00:21:06,083 --> 00:21:07,566
Down into the jaw.

143
00:21:13,029 --> 00:21:16,734
Still pouring in from above, the ball gently rotating.

144
00:21:19,077 --> 00:21:34,417
And we can feel its warm, golden, vibrant energy filling our throats.

145
00:21:34,438 --> 00:21:41,146
The whole head is now this golden ball, gently rotating.

146
00:21:43,017 --> 00:21:44,919
full of energy, warmth.

147
00:21:50,386 --> 00:22:06,207
Still pouring down from above, we can feel it beginning to spread over our shoulders and continuing to rotate, gently sinking into our chest.

148
00:22:17,694 --> 00:22:27,984
deep into our arms, deep into our chests, filling that whole area with warm golden delight.

149
00:22:35,211 --> 00:22:45,863
And it's still pouring down from above, down through the head, down the throat, into this ball gently rotating around our chest.

150
00:22:52,136 --> 00:23:05,421
And it continues downward, filling the rest of our arms, down to the elbows, filling that whole midriff, the stomach, that whole area, filling it with this warm golden delight.

151
00:23:21,719 --> 00:23:50,393
still pouring down from above, down through the head, down the arms, down the throat, down the chest, still pouring down from above, down through the head, down the throat, down the arms, the chest, into this ball, gently rotating around our stomach,

152
00:23:53,596 --> 00:24:04,955
And it continues to go downwards, gently turning, filling the whole abdomen with its warm, golden delight.

153
00:24:25,252 --> 00:24:40,730
still pouring down from above, down through the head, down the throat, down the arms, down the chest, through the stomach into this ball, gently rotating around the abdomen.

154
00:24:47,036 --> 00:24:48,577
And we feel it descending

155
00:24:48,877 --> 00:25:04,434
filling our hands, filling our hips, gently filling those areas with warm, vibrant, golden energy, spiralling downwards, slowly.

156
00:25:14,826 --> 00:25:17,028
We can feel it entering our knees,

157
00:25:26,729 --> 00:25:29,853
Downwards until we can feel it around our feet.

158
00:25:35,260 --> 00:25:38,464
Filling our feet with its warm golden energy.

159
00:25:42,490 --> 00:25:44,492
Still pouring in from above.

160
00:25:45,875 --> 00:25:49,901
Down through the head, down the throat, down the arms.

161
00:25:52,104 --> 00:25:55,048
Down through the chest, through the stomach, into the abdomen.

162
00:25:56,951 --> 00:26:03,877
down through the hips and legs, into this ball, gently rotating around our feet.

163
00:26:12,886 --> 00:26:14,508
So now we can use this energy.

164
00:26:15,229 --> 00:26:20,973
With the in-breath, draw that energy, with our own energy, up the spine to the top of the head.

165
00:26:21,934 --> 00:26:25,878
And there, let it join with all that energy still pouring down from above.

166
00:26:26,955 --> 00:26:30,523
And with the out-breath, let it all cascade down the body.

167
00:26:32,028 --> 00:26:36,719
Just breathing in and up, breathing out and down.

168
00:26:38,923 --> 00:26:42,332
Just breathing in and breathing out.

169
00:27:02,765 --> 00:27:09,895
And if there's a part of the body that needs special attention, let it pass through that part like water through a sponge.

170
00:27:28,823 --> 00:27:31,928
So now we can share this energy with individuals.

171
00:27:32,413 --> 00:27:36,753
by bringing people to mind and offering them our blessings.

172
00:28:03,548 --> 00:28:08,797
And finally, we can offer our blessings to all beings in all directions.

173
00:28:09,798 --> 00:28:16,328
Just breathing in, into the heart and breathing out to all beings.

174
00:28:19,914 --> 00:28:22,459
May all beings be free of physical pain.

175
00:28:25,964 --> 00:28:28,729
May all beings be free of mental distress.

176
00:28:32,522 --> 00:28:35,067
May all beings be liberated of all their suffering.

177
00:28:39,857 --> 00:28:41,981
May all beings be well and strong.

178
00:28:45,108 --> 00:28:47,854
May all beings treat their bodies wisely.

179
00:28:51,181 --> 00:28:54,227
May all beings strive diligently for their liberation.

180
00:28:58,644 --> 00:29:02,588
May all beings experience the peace and bliss of Nibbāna.

181
00:29:05,451 --> 00:29:23,049
Sābe satā sukītā hantu Sābe satā sukītā hantu

182
00:29:25,138 --> 00:29:34,086
Sāve sātā sukītā hantu.

